# __get__:    all false — no multiprocessing class is a descriptor.
# __set__:    all false — no multiprocessing class is a data descriptor.
# __delete__: all false — no multiprocessing class defines __delete__.
# All three descriptor protocol methods are absent from all eight classes' own __dict__.
